    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cafe Simulator is a business management simulation game where you build and operate your own cafe from the ground up. Start with a small coffee shop and transform it into a thriving business empire. Design your space, master the art of brewing, serve demanding customers, and compete with rival cafés in the city. Manage every aspect of your cafe from furniture placement to recipe creation as you grow your reputation and profits.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/fb35d338ca5790f2163cf067d96d9730.avif?t=1772200202\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras_big/fb35d338ca5790f2163cf067d96d9730.webp?t=1772200202 width=1560 height=394 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/5d857916d742b569aca4a7919e88c304.poster.avif?t=1772200202\" width=762 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/5d857916d742b569aca4a7919e88c304.webm?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the coffee brew skills and serve your customers efficiently. Operate various brewing tools, prepare different beverages using unique ingredients, and fulfill customer orders quickly to maximize satisfaction and earnings. Each drink requires proper equipment and ingredients ,unlock new recipes by purchasing specialized brewing tools and expanding your menu.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/6bdfb11b2f93cf805abcbfeca812465b.avif?t=1772200202\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras_big/6bdfb11b2f93cf805abcbfeca812465b.webp?t=1772200202 width=1560 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/fba73d170a2acf1f6ebeaad0019813b9.poster.avif?t=1772200202\" width=762 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/fba73d170a2acf1f6ebeaad0019813b9.webm?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a unique café that reflects your personal style. Choose from a wide variety of furniture including modern tables, leather chairs or whatever you want. Customize walls and flooring to match your vision. Place furniture strategically to maximize seating capacity while maintaining an appealing layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"> </span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/434d8d7b5b86413fa9d3460dfc28c51c.avif?t=1772200202\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras_big/434d8d7b5b86413fa9d3460dfc28c51c.webp?t=1772200202 width=1560 height=394 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0b936992a7117977d3ccf3916229b1dd.poster.avif?t=1772200202\" width=762 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0b936992a7117977d3ccf3916229b1dd.webm?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0b936992a7117977d3ccf3916229b1dd.mp4?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not the only café owner in the neighborhood. Monitor rival cafés, adapt your strategy to stay competitive, and use various tactics to dominate the local coffee scene. Engage with the city's biker gang for optional side activities including sabotaging competitor businesses. Competition is fierce ,only the smartest entrepreneurs will rise to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0874581cf916009c7a83e1618107623c.avif?t=1772200202\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras_big/0874581cf916009c7a83e1618107623c.webp?t=1772200202 width=1560 height=394 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/58c4b5b2bb738bca8c30663a59b09015.poster.avif?t=1772200202\" width=762 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/58c4b5b2bb738bca8c30663a59b09015.webm?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/58c4b5b2bb738bca8c30663a59b09015.mp4?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0ccd2b7a9814d3f3a63fd279a4028925.poster.avif?t=1772200202\" width=762 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0ccd2b7a9814d3f3a63fd279a4028925.webm?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384980/extras/0ccd2b7a9814d3f3a63fd279a4028925.mp4?t=1772200202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your café running smoothly while enjoying engaging mini-games. Clean your café through interactive mechanics, master the trash trick shot challenge to boost customer happiness, and participate in unique side activities. Take breaks from café management to explore unexpected opportunities ,including competitive chicken wrestling tournaments that reward you with money and reputation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
